eed="1200" data-delay="8000" data-title="Finer things"><img src="/img/slideshowImages/slider_image2.jpg" alt="" data-bgrepeat="no-repeat" data-bgfit="cover" data-bgparallax="7" class="rev-slidebg"><div class="tp-caption medium_text" data-x="center" data-y="center" data-voffset="-60" data-transform_idle="o:1;s:1000" data-transform_in="x:0;y:150;z:0;rotationZ:0;scaleX:1;scaleY:1;skewX:0;skewY:0;opacity:0;s:500;" data-transform_out="opacity:0;s:1000;e:Power3.easeInOut;" data-start="1000">Quality • Detail • Service</div><div class="tp-caption hero-text large_white" data-x="center" data-y="center" data-transform_idle="o:1;s:900" data-transform_in="x:0;y:150;z:0;rotationZ:0;scaleX:1;scaleY:1;skewX:0;skewY:0;opacity:0;s:500;" data-transform_out="opacity:0;s:1000;e:Power3.easeInOut;" data-start="1200">Focus on the finer things in Life</div><div class="tp-caption small_text" data-x="center" data-y="center" data-voffset="60" data-transform_idle="o:1;s:800" data-transform_in="x:0;y:150;z:0;rotationZ:0;scaleX:1;scaleY:1;skewX:0;skewY:0;opacity:0;s:500;" data-transform_out="opacity:0;s:1000;e:Power3.easeInOut;" data-start="1400">Trusted by hundreads of people in and around Santiniketan.</div><div class="tp-caption tp-resizeme" data-x="center" data-y="center" data-voffset="140" data-hoffset="-85" data-transform_idle="o:1;s:700" data-transform_in="x:0;y:150;z:0;rotationZ:0;scaleX:1;scaleY:1;skewX:0;skewY:0;opacity:0;s:500;" data-transform_out="opacity:0;s:1000;e:Power3.easeInOut;" data-start="1600" style="z-index: 12; max-width: auto; max-height: auto; white-space: nowrap"><a href="/avihita/#booking" class="btn btn-lg btn-white">Book Now</a></div><div class="tp-caption tp-resizeme" data-x="center" data-y="center" data-voffset="140" data-hoffset="89" data-transform_idle="o:1;s:700" data-transform_in="x:0;y:150;z:0;rotationZ:0;scaleX:1;scaleY:1;skewX:0;skewY:0;opacity:0;s:500;" data-transform_out="opacity:0;s:1000;e:Power3.easeInOut;" data-start="1600" style="z-index: 13; max-width: auto; max-height: auto; white-space: nowrap"><a href="/avihita/" class="btn btn-lg btn-transparent">Learn More</a></div></li></ul><div class="local-scroll"><a href="#intro" class="scroll-down"><i class="fa fa-angle-down"></i></a></div></div></div></section><section class="section-wrap intro" id="intro"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 text-center wow slideInUp" data-wow-duration="1.2s" data-wow-delay="0s"><p class="subheading">We believe that modern living in lifeless concrete jungles has alienated us from the sprawling greens; greys and blacks now dominate the landscape which was once filled with the myriad hues of life. To escape from this mundane lifestyle of the city, we are building urban settlements in Santiniketan, where the mornings would start with the chirping of birds, fragrance of flowers and cool breeze in communication with the sun-kissed greens.</p></div></div></div></section><section class="result-boxes"><div class="container-fluid"><div class="row"><div class="col-md-4 nopadding"><div class="statistic result-box result-box-first"><div class="result-wrap clearfix"><i class="icon icon-Heart"></i> <span class="timer" data-from="0" data-to="250">&nbsp;</span> <span>+</span> <span class="counter-text">Happy Families</span></div></div></div><div class="col-md-4 nopadding"><div class="statistic result-box result-box-second"><div class="result-wrap clearfix"><i class="icon icon-Speedometter"></i> <span class="timer" data-from="0" data-to="12">&nbsp;</span> <span>yrs</span> <span class="counter-text">Experience</span></div></div></div><div class="col-md-4 nopadding"><div class="statistic result-box result-box-third"><div class="result-wrap clearfix"><i class="icon icon-BigTruck"></i> <span class="timer" data-from="0" data-to="250000">&nbsp;</span> <span>+</span> <span class="counter-text">sqft. Constructed</span></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="section-wrap bg-light pb-mdm-50 pb-0" id="avihita"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 text-center"><a href="avihita/"><img src="/img/avihita_logo.png"></a></div></div><div class="row text-center"><h3 class="text-center bottom-line">Freedom lives within you, just let go!</h3></div><div class="row heading text-center"><p class="subheading">Rich with all modern amenities. Avihita ensures comfort for your outer being and calm for your inner peace. Once inside Avihita, you will meed some time to discover the entire spread of the layout. The vast openness will surprise you. The greenery will amaze you and you will love to venture outdoors around the complex that is studded with manicured gardens, but do not give away the essence of <strong>Santiniketan</strong>. <a href="/avihita/" class=""><br>Learn more..</a></p></div></div></section></div><section class="section-wrap promo-section pt-0 bg-light"><div id="owl-promo" class="owl-carousel owl-theme"><div class="item"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-md-8" data-wow-duration="2s" data-wow-delay="0.1s"><img src="/img/abihita/abihita11.jpg" alt=""></div><div class="col-md-4 promo-description"><p class="subheading"><strong>Avihita </strong>| Clear your mind</p><h3>The best of both worlds</h3><p class="mb-30">Rich with all modern ametities, Avihita ensures comfort for your outer being and calm for your inner soul. The greenery inside with all the manicured gardens will amaze you and give you the essence of <strong>Santiniketan</strong></p><a href="/avihita/#booking" class="btn btn-lg btn-color">Book Now</a> <a href="/avihita/" class="btn btn-lg btn-transparent btn-book">Learn More</a><div class="customNavigation mt-40"><a class="prev"><i class="icon arrow_left"></i></a> <a class="next"><i class="icon arrow_right"></i></a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="item"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-md-8" data-wow-duration="1s" data-wow-delay="0.1s"><a href="/avihita"><img src="/img/abihita/abihita4.jpg" alt="Avihita"></a></div><div class="col-md-4 promo-description"><p class="subheading"><strong>Avihita </strong>| Live Your Dream</p><h3>Discover the inside story</h3><p class="mb-30">There is a home for everyone at Avihita. Be it the cosy yet comfortable studio apartments or luxiourious bunglows, Avihita has it all. With all its modern amenities you can enjoy a modern lifestyle amidst the rural surroundings.</p><a href="/avihita/#booking" class="btn btn-lg btn-color">Book Now</a> <a href="/avihita/" class="btn btn-lg btn-transparent btn-book">Learn More</a><div class="customNavigation mt-40"><a class="prev"><i class="icon arrow_left"></i></a> <a class="next"><i class="icon arrow_right"></i></a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="item"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-md-8" data-wow-duration="2s" data-wow-delay="0.1s"><img src="/img/abihita/abihita5.jpg" alt=""></div><div class="col-md-4 promo-description"><p class="subheading"><strong>Avihita </strong>| Rich in culture</p><h3>Let the drama unfold</h3><p class="mb-30">A beautiful semi circular well planned open air theater will explore your happiness through fine expressions. You can arrange an open air drama or appreciate a lovely poem recitation.</p><a href="/avihita/#booking" class="btn btn-lg btn-color">Book Now</a> <a href="/avihita/" class="btn btn-lg btn-transparent btn-book">Learn More</a><div class="customNavigation mt-40"><a class="prev"><i class="icon arrow_left"></i></a> <a class="next"><i class="icon arrow_right"></i></a></div></div></div></div></div></div><section class="call-to-action bg-light"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-md-9 col-xs-12"><h2 style="font-weight: normal">With prices starting from <span style="font-weight: bold">₹10 lakhs</span>, theres something for every one!</h2></div><div class="col-md-3 col-xs-12 cta-button"><a href="/files/avihita_brochure.pdf" class="btn btn-lg btn-color" target="blank">Download Brochure</a></div></div></div></section></section><section class="section-wrap works-grid-3-col-wide pb-130 bg-dark" id="projects"><div class="container-fluid"><div class="row heading"><div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-4 col-sm-6 col-sm-offset-3"><h2 class="text-center bottom-line color-white">Previous Projects</h2><p class="subheading text-center" style="color: #6a6a6a">We Take Care For Every Detail</p></div></div><div class="grid-3-col grid-wide grid-gutter grayscale"><div class="work-item web-design print"><div class="work-img"><img src="/img/aapayan/aapayan1.jpg" alt=""><div class="work-overlay"><div class="work-description"><h3><a href="portfolio-single">Apayan</a></h3><span><a href="#">140+ apartments</a></span></div><a href="#" id="aapayan-gallery" class="btn btn-lg btn-transparent" title="Poster Mockup">View Project</a></div></div></div><div class="work-item web-design branding"><div class="work-img"><img src="/img/alapan/alapan6.jpg" alt=""><div class="work-overlay"><div class="work-description"><h3><a href="portfolio-single">Alapan</a></h3><span><a href="#">100 apartments</a></span></div><a href="#" id="alapan-gallery" class="mfp-iframe btn btn-lg btn-transparent">View Project</a></div></div></div><div class="work-item web-design branding"><div class="work-img"><img src="/img/parichoy/parichoy3.jpg" alt=""><div class="work-overlay"><div class="work-description"><h3><a href="portfolio-single">Parichoy</a></h3><span><a href="#">Humble beginings</a></span></div><a href="#" id="parichoy-gallery" class="lightbox-gallery mfp-iframe btn btn-lg btn-transparent">View Project</a></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="section-wrap pt-110" id="about-us"><div class="container"><div class="row heading"><div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3"><h2 class="text-center bottom-line">About Us</h2><p class="subheading text-center">Continuously Creating Beautiful Living Spaces</p></div></div><div class="row pb-130"><p class="intro-text text-center">Jhinuk Constructions is a well recognised and admired brand which has moved from strength to strength over the last decade. We stand firm on our commitment to provide affordable yet quality housing for every individual. Our strength lies in the delivery of promises through meticulous planning and a keen eye for quality and design. Convenient locations, quality materials, incredible workmanship and after sales service are some of the traits we strongly adhere to. So far we have innovated with various formats of residential housing projects and have created a great relationship with hundreds of happy home owners. We will strive to maintain the same zeal as we venture into broader domains and larger markets.</p></div><div class="row mt-minus-30 text-center"><h4>Our Vision</h4><p class="intro-text">Extensive urbanisation resulting from the economic development of the past decade has lead to a dearth of space in every Indian city. Our vision is to provide innovatively designed living spaces at an incredibly affordable price, thereby improving the lifestyle of every deserving citizen of the country.</p></div></div></section><section class="section-wrap parallax-testimonials" style="background-image: url(img/slideshowImages/specs.jpg)"><div id="owl-testimonials" class="owl-carousel owl-theme text-center"><div class="item"><div class="container testimonial"><div class="row"><div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1"><i class="fa fa-quote-left"></i><p class="testimonial-text">Appayan has been a world class experience and home away from home in Bolpur. Appayan truly welcomes its residents soulfully. The buildings' finer architecture and ambience have been a treat; not to forget the amply spacious park, community hall, gym and library. This housing complex has been build with style and designed with poise. Buying a home for myself was a dream, Appayan was a truly affordable and worthy investment. This decision has resulted in lifelong relationships with the co-residences and the builder. Jhinuk Constructions builds relationships and I am happy to be a member of this family build with love and care.</p><h6>Dr. Subhashree Sanyal</h6><span>Assistant Professor of Social Work, Visva Bharati University</span></div></div></div></div><div class="item"><div class="container testimonial"><div class="row"><div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1"><i class="fa fa-quote-left"></i><p class="testimonial-text">My dream of owning a flat in Santiniketan , finally came true when I became the proud owner of Appayan Flat by Jhinuk Construction . Certain things are very difficult to define especially, when it exceeds the expectations. The quality of work and materials used by the builder is very good. The professional approach and dedication of the staffs of Jhinuk Constructions is highly appreciated. While taking over the apartment. they have noted all the changes that I mentioned to them and executed them to my entire satisfaction. I wish Jhinuk Construction success in their future endeavours.</p><h6>Dr. Avijit Banerjee</h6><span>Associate Professor and Head, Department of Chinese Language and Culture (Cheena Bhavana), Visva-Bharati University</span></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="section-wrap contact" id="contact"><div class="container"><div class="row heading"><div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 text-center"><h2 class="text-center bottom-line">Contact Us</h2><p class="subheading">Don't hesitate to get in touch please fill out this form and we'll get back to you within 48hrs.</p></div></div><div class="row"><div class="col-md-4"><h5>Get in Touch</h5><p>Mon-Fri: 10:00 – 17:00</p><div class="contact-item"><div class="contact-icon"><i class="icon icon-Pointer"></i></div><h6>Address</h6><p>JHINUK CONSTRUCTIONS,<br>SuperMarket, Block A,<br>Bolpur, Birbhum,<br>PIN: 731204</p></div><div class="contact-item"><div class="contact-icon"><i class="icon icon-Phone"></i></div><h6>Call Us</h6><span><a href="tel:03463252512">03463-252512</a></span></div><div class="contact-item"><div class="contact-icon"><i class="icon icon-Mail"></i></div><h6>E-mail</h6><a href="mailto:jhinukconstructions@gmail.com">jhinukconstructions@gmail.com</a></div></div><div class="col-md-8"><form id="contact-form" action="#"><div class="row contact-row"><div class="col-md-6 contact-name"><input name="name" id="name" type="text" placeholder="Your Full Name" required="required"></div><div class="col-md-6 contact-email"><input name="contact" id="contact" type="tel" placeholder="Contact Number" required="required"></div></div><input name="email" id="email" type="email" placeholder="Your eMail id" required="required"><textarea name="comment" id="comment" placeholder="How can we help you?" required="required"></textarea><input type="submit" class="btn btn-lg btn-color btn-submit" value="Send Message" id="submit-message"><div id="msg" class="message"></div></form></div></div></div></section><section class="section-wrap pb-0 pt-0"><div class="row heading"><div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 text-center"><h2 class="text-center bottom-line">Office Location</h2><p class="subheading">The Office is located on the 1st floor of Bolpur SuperMarket (Block A)</p></div></div><div id="google-map" class="gmap" data-address="ChIJYUaKHbTc-TkR0o_XvhM7xbU&key=AIzaSyCXvK62_JQ1ovhatpCXpH12mrQevp_WIto"></div></section><footer class="footer minimal bg-dark"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-4"><div class="footer-logo local-scroll" data-wow-duration="1s" data-wow-delay="0.2s"><h2><a href="#home" class="color-white"><img src="/img/logo.png" width="120px" style="opacity: 0.4"></a><br><br></h2></div></div></div><div class="row"><span class="copyright text-center">©2017 Jhinuk Constructions | Development by <a href="http://swrdfish.github.io/" target="blank">Binayak</a> & <a href="http://ghoshbishakh.github.io/" target="blank">Bishakh</a></span><br><span class="copyright text-center">This site only describes the intent, purpose and concept of Jhinuk Constr